/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: user_friend */
/*==============================================================*/
create table user_friend
(
open_id varchar(50) not null,
friend_open_id varchar(50) not null,
last_contact varchar(500),
create_time timestamp,
modify_time timestamp,
primary key (open_id, friend_open_id)
);
